hadiths[43]{hadithnumber,text}:
2440,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jab mominon ko dozakh se nijat mil jaeygi to unhein aik pul par jo jannat aur dozakh ke darmyan hoga rok liya jaeyga aur wahin unke mazaalim ka badla de diya jaeyga jo wo duniya mein aapas mein kartey they. phir jab paak saaf ho jaeinge to unhein jannat mein daakhile ki ijazat di jaeygi. us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai, unmein se har shakhs apne jannat ke ghar ko apne duniya ke ghar se bhi behtar taur par pahchaanega. Yoonus-bin-Muhammad ne bayan kya ke ham se Sheban ne bayan kya, unse Qatada ne aur unse abu-mutwakkil ne bayan kya."
2441,"main Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke hath mein hath diye ja raha tha. ke aik shakhs samney aaya aur puchha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aap ne (qiyamat mein Allah aur bandey ke darmyan honey wali) sargoshi ke barey mein kya suna hai? Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke Allah Taala momin ko apne nazdeek bula lega aur is par apna parda daal dega aur usey chipa lega. Allah Taala us se farmaeyga kya tujh ko falan gunah yad hai? kya falan gunah tujh ko yad hai? wo momin kahega haan, aey mere parwardigaar! aakhir jab wo apne gunahon ka iqrar kar lega aur usey yaqin aa jaeyga ke ab wo halaak hua to Allah Taala farmaeyga ke maine duniya mein terey gunahon par parda daala aur aaj bhi main teri maghfirat karta hun, chunanche usey uski nekiyon ki kitab de di jaeygi, lekin kaafir aur munafiq ke mutaalliq un par gawah (malaaika, anbiyaa, aur tamam jin w insan sab) kahengey ke yahi wo log hain jinhoney apne parwardigar par jhoot baandha tha. khabardaar ho jaao! zaalimon par Allah ki phitkar hogi."
2442,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aik musalman doosrey musalman ka bhai hai, to is par zulm na karey aur na zulm honey de. jo shakhs apne bhai ki zarurat poori karey, Allah Taala uski zarurat poori karega. jo shakhs kisi musalman ki aik museebat ko door karey, Allah Taala uski qiyamat ki museebaton mein se aik badi museebat ko door farmaeyga aur jo shakhs kisi musalman ke aib ko chhipaaey Allah Taala qiyamat mein uske aib chhipaaeyga."
2443,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, apne bhai ki madad karo wo zaalim ho ya mazloom."
2444,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, apne bhai ki madad karo chahe wo zaalim ho ya mazloom. sahaba ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah! ham mazloom ki to madad kar saktey hain. lekin zaalim ki madad kis tarah karein? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke zulm se uska hath pakad lo (yahii uski madad hai)."
2445,"hamein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saat (7) chizon ka hukm farmaya tha aur saat (7) hi chizon se mana bhi farmaya tha (jin chizon ka hukm farmaya tha un mein) unhon-ne mareez ki iyaadat, janazey ke peechhey chalney, chheenkney waley ka jawab dene, salam ka jawab dene, mazloom ki madad karne, dawat karne waley (ki da'wat) qabool karne, aur qism poori karne ka zikr kya."
2446,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik momin doosrey momin ke sath aik Imaarat ke hukm mein hai ke aik ko doosrey se quwwat pahunchti hai. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne aik hath ki ungliyon ko doosrey hath ki ungliyon ke andar kya.
2447,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, zulm qiyamat ke din andherey hongey."
2448,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko jab (aamil bana kar) Yaman bhejaa, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hidayat farmai ke mazloom ki baddua se dartey rehna ke us (dua'a) ke aur Allah Taala ke darmyan koi parda nahi hota."
2449,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, agar kisi shakhs ka zulm kisi doosrey ki izzat par ho ya kisi tareeqe (se zulm kya ho) to aaj hii, us din ke aaney se pahley maaf kara ley jis din na Dinar hongey, na dirham, balke agar uska koi nek amal hoga to uske zulm ke badley mein wahi ley liya jaeyga aur agar koi nek amal uske paas nahi hoga to uske (mazloom) sathi ki buraaiyaan is par daal di jaaeingii. Abu-Abdullah (Imam Bukhari (rh)) ne kaha ke Ismaaeel-bin-abii-Ovais ne kaha Saeed Maqbari ka naam Maqbari isliye hua ke qabristaan ke qareeb unhon-ne qiyam kya tha. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke Saeed Maqbari hi banii-Leis ke ghulam hain. pura naam Saeed-bin-abii-Saeed hai aur (unke waalid) abu-Saeed ka naam kaisaan hai."
2450,(qur'aan Majeed ki aayat) (وإن امرأة خافت من بعلها نشوزا أو إعراضا) ''agar koi aurat apne shauhar ki taraf se nafrat ya uske munh pherney ka khof rakhti ho'' ke barey mein farmaya ke kisi shakhs ki biwi hai lekin shauhar uske paas zyada aata jata nahi balke usey juda karna chahta hai is par uski biwi kehti hai ke main apna haq tumhen maaf karti hun. usi barey mein ye aayat nazil hui.
2451,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein doodh ya pani peeney ko pesh kya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey piyaa . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daain taraf aik ladka tha aur baain taraf badi umr waley they. ladkey se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tum mujhey uski ijazat doge ke un logon ko ye ( piyala ( de dun? ladkey ne kaha, nahi Allah ki qasam! ya Rasulullah! aap ki taraf se milney waley hissey ka eisaar main kisi par nahi kar sakta. rawi ne bayan kya ke aakhir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo piyala usi ladkey ko de diya."
2452,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jisne kisi ki zameen zulm se ley li, usey qiyamat ke din saat (7) zameenon ka tauq pahnaayaa jaeyga"
2453,"unke aur kuchh doosrey logon ke darmyan (zameen ka ( jhagdaa tha. iska zikr unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kya to unhon-ne batlaayaa, abu-Salma! zameen se parhez kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, agar kisi shakhs ne aik baalisht bhar zameen bhi kisi doosrey ki zulm se ley li to saat (7) zameenon ka tauq (qiyamat ke din) uske gardan mein daala jaeyga"
2454,"(Abdullaah-bin-Umar (rz)) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jis shakhs ne nahaq kisi zameen ka thoda sa hissey bhi ley liya, to qiyamat ke din usey saat (7) zameenon tak dhansaayaa jaeyga abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke ye hadis Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ki is kitab mein nahi hai jo khuraasaan mein thi. balke usmein thi jisey unhon-ne Basra main apne shagirdon ko imlaa karaya tha."
2455,ham kuchh Iraq walon ke sath Madina mein muqeem they. wahan hamein qahat mein mubtala hona padaa . Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) khaney ke liye hamarey paas khajoor bhijwaayaa kartey they. aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab hamari taraf se guzartey to farmatey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (doosrey logon ke sath mil kar khaatey waqt) 2 khajoor ko aik sath mila kar khaney se mana farmaya hai magar ye ke tum mein se koi shakhs apne bhai se ijazat ley ley.
2456,"Ansar mein aik sahabi jinhein abu-Shuaib (Raziallahu anhu) kaha jata tha, ka aik qasaaii ghulam tha. abu-Shuaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke mere liye panch aadmiyon ka khana taiyaar kar de, kyonke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko char doosrey ashaab ke sath dawat doonga. unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak par bhook ke aasaar dekhey they. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unhon-ne batlaayaa. aik aur shakhs Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bin bulaey chala gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saahibe-khaana se farmaya ye aadmi bhi hamarey sath aa gaya hai. kya uske liye tumhari ijazat hai? unhon-ne kaha ji haan ijazat hai."
2457,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Allah Taala ke yahan sabse zyada na-pasand wo aadmi hai jo sakht jhagdaaloo ho."
2458,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hujrey ke darwazey ke samney jhagdey ki awaz suni aur jhagdaa karne walon ke paas tashrif laey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke main bhi aik insan hun. isliye jab mere yahan koi jhagdaa lekar aata hai to ho sakta hai ke (fareeqain mein se) aik fareeq ki bahas doosrey fareeq se umda ho, main samajhta hun ke wo sachcha hai. aur is tarah main uske haq mein faisla kar deta hun, lekin agar main usko (iske zahiri bayan par bharosa karke) kisi musalman ka haq dila dun to dozakh ka aik tukda usko dila raha hun, wo ley-ley ya chhod de."
2459,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya char khaslatein aisi hain ke jis shakhs mein bhi wo hongii, wo munafiq hoga. ya un char mein se agar aik khaslat bhi usmein hai to usmein nifaq ki aik khaslat hai. yahan tak ke wo usey chhod de. jab boley to jhoot boley, jab wada karey to pura na karey, jab muaahida karey to bewafaaii karey, aur jab jhagdey to bad zabani par utar aaey."
2460,"Utba-bin- Rabee ki beti Hind (Raziallahu anhu) haazire-khidmat huin aur arz kya, ya Rasulullah! Abu-Sufiyan (jo unke shauhar hain wo ( kanjoos hain. to kya ismein koi harj hai agar main unke maal mein se lekar apne baal bachchon ko khilaaya karun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum dastoor ke mutabiq unke maal se lekar khilaao to usmein koi harj nahi."
2461,"ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya aap hamein mukhtalif mulk walon ke paas bhejtey hain aur) kuchh baar ( hamein aisey logon ke paas jana padta hai ke wo hamari ziyaafat tak nahi kartey. aap ki aisey mauqon par kya hidayat hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya, agar tumhara qiyam kisi qabeeley mein ho aur tum se aisa bartaw kya jaey jo kisi mehman ke liye munasib hai to tum usey qabool kar lo, lekin agar wo na karein to tum khud mehmani ka haq unse wsool kar lo."
2462,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, jab apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Allah Taala ne wafat de di to Ansar banu- saaida ke) Saqeefa ( chaupaal mein jama huey. maine Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke aap hamein bhi wahin ley chaliye . chunanche ham Ansar ke yahaan Saqeefa-banu-Saaida mein pahunchey."
2463,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, koi shakhs apne padosi ko apni diwar mein khoontii gaadney se na rokey. phir Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they, ye kya baat hai ke main tumhen us se munh pherney wala paata hun. qism Allah ki! us khoontii ko tumharey kandhon ke darmyan gaad doonga."
2464,"main abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke makan mein logon ko sharab pilaa raha tha. un dinon khajoor hi ki sharab piyaa kartey they. (phir junhii sharab ki hurmat par Quran ki aayat utri ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik munaadii se eilaan karaya ke sharab haram ho gaee hai. unhon-ne kaha (ye suntey hi ( abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke bahar ley ja kar us sharab ko baha de. chunanche maine bahar nikal kar saari sharab baha di. sharab Madina ki galiyon mein bahney lagii, to kuchh logon ne kaha, yun malum hota hai ke bahut se log us haalat mein qatl kar diye gaey hain ke sharab unke pet mein maujood thi. phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai (ليس على الذين آمنوا وعملوا الصالحات جناح فيما طعموا) ''wo log jo eman laey aur amale-Saaleh kiye, un par un chizon ka koi gunah nahi hai. jo pahley kha chukey hain ( aakhir aayat tak) ."
2465,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya raston mein baithney se bacho. sahaba ne arz kya ke ham to wahan baithney par majbur hain. wahi hamarey baithney ki jagah hoti hai ke jahan ham baatein kartey hain. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar wahan baithney ki majboorii hi hai to rastey ka haq bhi ada karo. sahaba ne puchha aur rastey ka haq kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, nigaah neechi rakhna, kisi ko takleef deney se bachnaa, salam ka jawab denaa, achi baton ke liye logon ko hukm karna aur buri baton se roknaa."
2466,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aik shakhs rastey main safar kar raha tha ke usey piyaas lagi phir usey rastey mein aik kunwaan mila aur wo uske andar utar gaya aur pani piyaa. jab bahar aaya to uski nazar aik kuttey par padi jo haanp raha tha aur piyaas ki sakhti se keechad chaat raha tha. us shakhs ne sochaa ke us waqt ye kutta bhi piyaas ki itni hi shiddat mein mubtala hai jis mein main tha. chunanche wo phir kuwein mein utra aur apne jootey mein pani bhar kar us ne kuttey ko pilaayaa. Allah Taala ke yahan uska ye amal maqbool hua aur uski maghfirat kar di gaee. sahaba ne poochha, ya Rasulullah kya janwaron ke silsile mein bhi hamein ajr milta hai? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, har jaandaar makhlooq ke silsiley mein ajr milta hai."
2467,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina ke aik buland makan par chadhey . phir farmaya, kya tum log bhi dekh rahe ho jo main dekh raha hun ke (an-qareeb) tumharey gharon mein fitney is tarah baras rahe hongey jaisey barish barastii hai."
2468,"mein hamesha is baat ka aarzu-mand rehta tha ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki un 2 beeviyon ke naam poochhoon jinke barey mein Allah Taala ne ( sura Tahreem mein) farmaya hai) إن تتوبا إلى الله فقد صغت قلوبكما‏ ( ''agar tum donon Allah ke samney tauba karo (to behtar hai) ke tumharey dil bigad gaey hain.'' phir main unke sath Haj ko gaya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) rastey se qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye hatey to main bhi unke sath (paanii ka eik) chhaagal lekar gaya. phir wo qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye chaley gaey aur jab wapas aaey to maine unke donon hathon par chhaagal se pani daala aur unhon-ne wuzu kya, phir maine poochha, ya ameerul-momineen ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon mein wo 2 khawaateen kon si hain jinke mutaalliq Allah Taala ne ye farmaya ke) إن تتوبا إلى الله‏ ( ''tum donon Allah ke samney tauba karo '' unhon-ne farmaya, Ibne-Abbas ! tum par hairat hai. wo to Aaisha aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) hain. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) meri taraf mutwajjeh ho kar pura waqia bayan karne lagey. aap ne batlaya ke banu-Umaiya bin Zaid ke qabeeley mein jo Madina se mila hua tha. main apne aik Ansari padosi ke sath rehta tha. ham donon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein haziri ki baari muqarrar kar rakhi thi. aik din wo hazir hotey aur aik din main. jab main haziri deta to us din ki tamam khabrein wghaira laataa (aur unko sunata (aur jab wo hazir hotey to wo bhi isi tarah kartey. ham Quraish ke log (Makka mein) apni aurton par ghalib raha kartey they. lekin jab ham ( hijrat karke ( Ansar ke yahan aaey to unhein dekha ke unki auratein khud un par ghalib thin. hamari aurton ne bhi unka tariqa ikhtiyar karna shuru kar diya. maine aik din apni biwi ko daantaa to unhon-ne bhi iska jawab diya. unka ye jawab mujhey na-gawar malum hua. lekin unhon-ne kaha ke main agar jawab deti hun to tumhen na-gawari kyon hoti hai. qism Allah ki! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyan tak aapko jawab de deti hain aur kuchh beeviyan to aap se poorey din aur poori raat khafa rehti hain. is baat se main bahut ghabraayaa aur maine kaha ke unmein se jisne bhi aisa kya hoga wo bahut badey nuqsan aur khasaarey mein hai. iske baad maine kapdey pahney aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ( umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki sahibzadi aur Ummul-Momenin (ke paas pahuncha aur kaha aey Hafsa ! kya tum mein se koi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poorey din-raat tak naraz rehti hain. unhon-ne kaha ke haan! main bol utha ke phir to wo tabahi aur nuqsan mein rahiin. kya tumhen us se amn hai ke Allah Taala apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki narazgi ki wjah se (tum par) ghussa ho jaey aur tum halaak ho jao . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zyada chizon ka mutalba hargiz na kya karo, na kisi maamle mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kisi baat ka jawab do aur na aap par narazgi ka izhar honey do, albatta jis cheez ki tumhen zarurat ho, wo mujh se maang liya karo, kisi khud faraibi mein mubtala na rehna, tumhari ye padausan tum se zyada jameel aur naazuk hain aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zyada pyari bhi hain. aap ki murad Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se thi. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, un dinon ye charcha ho raha tha ke ghassaan ke fauji ham se ladney ke liye ghodon ko sum laga rahe hain. mere padosi aik din apni baari par Madina gaey huey they. phir isha ke waqt wapas lautey. aa kar mera darwaza unhon-ne badi zor se khatkhataayaa, aur kaha kya aap so gaey hain? main bahut ghabraayaa hua bahar aaya unhon-ne kaha ke aik bahut bada haadisa pesh aa gaya hai. maine puchha kya hua? kya ghassaan ka lashkar aa gayaa? unhon-ne kaha balke us se bhi bada aur sangeen haadisa, wo ye ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ko talaaq de di. ye sun kar umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, Hafsa to tabah w barbad ho gaee. mujhey to pahley hi khatkaa tha ke kahin aisa na ho jaey (Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha) phir maine kapdey pahney. subah ki Namaz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath padhi (namaz padhtey hi) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne bula khaana mein tashrif le gaey aur wahin tanhai ikhtiyar kar li. main Hafsa ke yahan gaya, dekha to wo ro rahi thin, maine kaha, ro kyon rahi ho? kya pahley hi maine tumhen nahi keh diya tha? kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tum sab ko talaaq de di hai? unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey kuchh malum nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baalaa-khaane mein tashrif rakhtey hain. phir main bahar nikla aur member ke paas aaya. wahan kuchh log maujood they aur kuchh ro bhi rahe they. thodi der to main unke sath betha raha. lekin mujh par ranj ka ghalba hua, aur main baalaa-khaaney ke paas pahuncha, jis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif rakhtey they. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik siyah ghulam se kaha, (ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaho (ke umr ijazat chahta hai. wo ghulam andar gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se guftgu karke wapas aaya aur kaha ke maine aap ki baat pahuncha di thi, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho gaey, chunanche main wapas aa kar unhiin logon ke sath baith gaya jo member ke paas maujood they. phir mujh par ranj ghalib aaya aur main dobara aaya. lekin us baar bhi wahi hua. phir aa kar unhiin logon mein baith gaya jo member ke paas they. lekin us martaba phir mujh se nahi raha gaya aur maine ghulam se aa kar kaha, ke umr ke liye ijazat chaaho. lekin baat joon ki toon rahi. jab main wapas ho raha tha ke ghulam ne mujh ko pukara aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aapko ijazat de di hai. main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khajoor ki chatai par letey huey they. jis par koi bistar bhi nahi tha. isliye chatai ke ubhrey huey hisson ka nishan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pahlu mein pad gaya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt aik aisey takiye par tek lagaey huey they jiske andar khajoor ki chhaal bhari gaee thi. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya aur khadey hi khadey arz ki, ke kya aap ne apni beeviyon ko talaaq de di hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nigaah meri taraf karke farmaya ke nahi. maine aap ke gham ko halka karne ki koshish ki aur kehney laga. . . . ab bhi main khada hi tha. . . . ya Rasulullah ! aap jantey hi hain ke ham Quraish ke log apni beeviyon par ghalib rahtey they, lekin jab ham aik aisi qaum mein aagey jinki auratein un par ghalib thin, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne tafseel zikr ki. is baat par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraa diye. phir maine kaha, main Hafsa ke yahan bhi gaya tha aur us se keh aaya tha ke kahin kisi khud faraibi mein na mubtala rehna. ye tumhari padausan tum se zyada khoobsurat aur paak hain aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zyada mahboob bhi hain. aap Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf ishara kar rahe they. is baat par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dobara muskuraa diye. jab maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko muskuratey dekha, to (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ( baith gaya aur aap ke ghar mein charon taraf dekhney laga. b-khudaa ! siwaey teen khaalon ke aur koi cheez wahan nazar na aai. maine kaha, ya Rasulullah ! aap Allah Taala se dua farmaiye ke wo aap ki ummat ko kushadgi ata farma de. Faaris aur Rome (mojooda Itly) ke log to poori faraakhii ke sath rahtey hain. duniya unhein khub mili hui hai. halanke wo Allah Taala ki ibadat bhi nahi kartey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tek lagaey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey khttaab ke betey! kya tumhen abhi kuchh shuba hai? (tu duniya ki daulat ko achi samajhta hai) ye to aisey log hain ke unke achchhey aamaal (jo wo maamlaat ki had tak kartey hain unki jazaa) isi duniya mein unko de di gaee hai. (ye sun kar) main bol utha . ya Rasulullah ! mere liye Allah se maghfirat ki dua kijiye . to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (apni beeviyon se) is baat par alehadgii ikhtiyar kar li thi ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne posheeda baat keh di thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us intihai narazgi ki wjah se jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hui thi, farmaya tha ke main ab unke paas aik mahiney tak nahi jaaunga aur yahi mauqa hai jis par Allah Taala ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mutanabbeh (aagaah) kya tha. phir jab untees din guzar gaey to aap Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar tashrif le gaey aur unhiin ke yahan se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shuruaat ki. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke aap ne to ahad kya tha ke hamarey yahan aik mahiney tak nahi tashrif laaengey aur aaj abhi untiswin ki subah hai. main to din gin rahi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ye mahina untees din ka hai aur wo mahina untees hi din ka tha. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir wo aayat nazil hui jis mein (nabi ki beeviyon ko) ikhtiyar diya gaya tha. uski bhi shuruaat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh hi se ki aur farmaya ke main tum se aik baat kehta hun, aur ye zaroori nahi ke jawab fauran do, balke apne waalidain se bhi mashwara kar lo. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke aapko ye malum tha ke mere maan-baap kabhi aap se judai ka mashwara nahi de saktey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne farmaya hai ke ''aey nabii! apni beeviyon se keh do'' Allah Taala ke qaul عظیما tak. maine arz kya kya ab us mamley mein bhi main apne waalidain se mashwara karne jaaungii! usmein to kisi shubeh ki gunjaaish hi nahi hai. ke main Allah aur uske rasool aur daare-aakhirat ko pasand karti hun. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni dusri beeviyon ko bhi ikhtiyar diya aur unhon-ne bhi wahi jawab diya jo Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne diya tha."
2469,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ke paas aik mahina tak na janey ki qism khaaii thi, aur (iilaa ke waqia se pahley 5 H mein) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qadam Mubarak mein moch aa gaee thi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne bula khaane mein thahre huey huey they. (iilaa ke mauqe par) umr (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur arz kya, ya Rasulullah! kya aap ne apni beeviyon ko talaaq de di hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. albatta aik mahiney ke liye unke paas na janey ki qism kha li hai. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) untees din tak beeviyon ke paas nahi gaey (aur untees taareekh ko hi chaand ho gaya tha) isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baalaa-khaaney se utrey aur beeviyon ke paas gaey."
2470,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif rakhtey they. isliye main bhi masjid ke andar chala gaya. albatta oont balaat ke aik kinarey par baandh diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maine arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! aap ka oont hazir hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur oont ke charon taraf tahalney lagey. phir farmaya ke qeemat bhi ley aur oont bhi ley jaa.
2471,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, ya ye kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik qaum ki koodi par tashrif laaey, aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahan khadey ho kar peshab kya."
2472,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aik shakhs rastey par chal raha tha ke usne wahan kaantey daar dali dekhi. us ne usey utha liya to Allah Taala ne uska ye amal qabool kya aur uski maghfirat kar di."
2473,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne faisla kya tha jabke rastey (ki zameen) ke barey mein jhagdaa ho to saat (7) hath rasta chhod dena chahiye
2474,"maine Abdullah-bin Yazeed Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, jo Adii-bin-Saabit ke naana they. ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne loot-maar karne aur musla karne se mana farmaya tha."
2475,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, zaanii momin rahtey huey zina nahi kar sakta. sharab peeneywaalaa momin rahtey huey sharab nahi pi sakta. chor momin rahtey huey chori nahi kar sakta aur koi shakhs momin rahtey huey loot aur ghaarat garii nahi kar sakta ke logon ki nazrein uski taraf uthi hui hon aur wo lot raha ho, Saeed aur abu-Salma ki bhi Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se b-hawaala Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isi tarah riwayat hai, albatta unki riwayat mein loot ka tazkira nahi hai."
2476,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim na hogi jab tak ibne-Maryam ka nuzool aik aadil hukmaraan ki haisiyat se tum mein na ho jaey. wo saleeb ko tod dengey, suwaron ko qatl kar dengey aur jiziya qabool nahi karengey. (us daur mein) maal w daulat ki itni kasarat ho jaeygi ke koi qabool nahi karega."
2477,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par dekha ke aag jalaaii ja rahi hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ye aag kis liye jalaaii ja rahi hai? sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke gadhey (ka gosht pakaaney (ke liye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo bartan (jis mein gadhey ka gosht ho ( tod 2 aur gosht phenk do. is par sahaba boley aisa kyon na kar lein ke gosht to phenk dein aur bartan dho lein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bartan dho lo. abu-Adbullah."
2478,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (fatah Makka ke din jab) Makka mein dakhil huey to khaana Kaba ke charon taraf 360 but they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein aik chhadi thi jis se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un buton par maarney lagey aur farmaney lagey ke (جاء الحق وزهق الباطل) '' haq aa gaya aur baatil mit gaya '' .
2479,unhon-ne apne hujrey ke saaybaan par aik parda latkaa diya jis mein tasweerein bani hui thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (jab dekha to) usey utaar kar phaad dala. (Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) phir maine us pardey se 2 gaddey bana daley. wo donon gaddey ghar mein rahtey they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un par betha kartey they.
2480,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs apne maal ki hifazat kartey huey qatl kar diya gaya wo Shahid hai."
2481,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) paak beeviyon mein se kisi aik ke yahan tashrif rakhtey they. ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) mein se aik ne wahin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye khaadim ke hath aik pyaley mein kuchh khaney ki cheez bhijwaai . unhon-ne aik hath us pyaley par maaraa, aur piyala ( gir kar) toot gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pyaley ko joda aur jo khaney ki cheez thi usmein dobara rakh kar sahaba se farmaya ke khaao. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne piyala laney waley (khaadim ( ko rok liya aur piyala bhi nahi bhejaa. balke jab ( khaney se) sab farigh ho gaey to doosra achchha piyala bhijwa diya aur jo toot gaya tha usey nahi bhijwaayaa. ibne-abii-Maryam ne bayan kya ke hamein Yahyaa-bin-Ayyoob ne khabar di, unse Humaid ne bayan kya, unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne."
2482,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Bani-Israeel mein aik sahib they, jinka naam Juraij tha. wo Namaz padh rahe they ke unki walida aaiin aur unhein pukaaraa. unhon-ne jawab nahi diya. sochtey rahe ke jawab dun ya Namaz padhun. phir wo dobara aaiin aur (ghussey mein) baddua kar gaiin. aey Allaah! usey maut na aaey jab tak kisi badkaar aurat ka munh na dekh ley. Juraij apne ibadat khaney mein rahtey they. aik aurat ne (jo Juraij ke ibadat khaney ke paas apni maweshii charaayaa karti thi aur faahisha thi) kaha ke Juraij ko fitna mein daley baghair na rahoongii. chunanche wo unke samney aai aur guftgu karni chaahii, lekin unhon-ne munh pher liya. phir wo aik charwaahey ke paas gaee aur apne jism ko uske qaabu mein de diya. aakhir ladka paida hua aur us aurat ne ilzam lagaya ke ye Juraij ka ladka hai. qaum ke log Juraij ke yahan aaey aur unka ibadat khaana tod diya. unhein bahar nikala aur gaaliyaan din. lekin Juraij ne wuzu kya aur Namaz padh kar us ladkey ke paas aaey. unhon-ne us se poochha. bachchey! tumhara bap kon hai? bachcha ( Allah ke hukm se) bol padaa ke charwaahaa! (qaum khush ho gaee aur) kaha ke ham aap ke liye soney ka ibadat khaana banwaa dein. Juraij ne kaha ke mera ghar to mitti hi se banega."
